{"lemma":"ظَنِينُو","slug":"ظَنِينُو","root":"ظ.ن.ن","root_slug":"ظ-ن-ن","root_link":"/words/roots/ظ-ن-ن","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n27700"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B8%D9%8E%D9%86%D9%90%D9%8A%D9%86%D9%8F%D9%88"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n27700","headword_ar":"ظَنِينٌ","root":"Zn","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Suspected;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, Mgh, Msb, K;) applied to a man; (S, M;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maZonuwnN","text_ar":"مَظْنُونٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mbr, Msb,) in this sense: (Msb:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aZin~aA='u","text_ar":"اَظِنَّا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, TA.) Thus in the saying in the Kur [lxxxi. 24],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wamaA huwa EalaY A@logayobi biZaniynK","text_ar":"وَمَا هُوَ عَلَى ا@لْغَيْبِ بِظَنِينٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, M, Msb,) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And he is not suspected as to"},{"kind":"text","text":"what he makes known from God, of the knowledge of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that which is undiscoverable,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as is related on the authority of 'Alee: or, accord. to Fr, it may mean"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weak;"},{"kind":"text","text":"for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZaniynN","text_ar":"ظَنِينٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"may have this meaning like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZanuwnN","text_ar":"ظَنُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"has: (T:) some read"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biDanynK","text_ar":"بِضَنينٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dn","text_ar":"ضن"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ahaAdapu ZaniynK","text_ar":"شَهَادَةُ ظَنِينٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is said in a trad. to be not allowable, is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The testimony of one who is suspected"},{"kind":"text","text":"as to his religion. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nafosN","text_ar":"نَفْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zan~aA='u","text_ar":"ظَنَّا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"means ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A soul,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"person,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"suspected."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  Also One"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who treats"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"regards another,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"others, with enmity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hostility;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, M;) because of his evil opinion and the evil opinion of which he is an object. (M.) ―         -b3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZanuwnN","text_ar":"ظَنُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":["Mbr","Msb","T","M"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}